## 📡 Application Flow

```
User Input
    ↓
Streamlit UI
    ↓
LangChain
    ↓
OpenAI GPT Model
    ↓
Response Generated
    ↓
Display in Streamlit
```

---

## 🔒 Security Best Practices

Never upload `.env` file to GitHub.

Add `.env` to `.gitignore`:

```
.env
venv/
__pycache__/
```

